    <string name="section_garmin_setup">Garmin Connect Setup</string>
    <string name="garmin_setup_instructions">To see transliterated text on your Garmin watch:\n\n1. Open Garmin Connect\n2. Menu → Garmin Devices → your device\n3. Device Settings → Notifications\n4. Enable \"NotifHay\" in the app list\n5. Disable the original apps (Telegram, WhatsApp, etc.) from the list — otherwise the watch shows both the original and the transliterated notification\n\nAll Armenian text is transliterated automatically. Other languages pass through unchanged.</string>

